dct_title_s: Greece: roads and ports / published by the Office of Strategic Services. Research and Analysis Branch.
dct_description_sm: Map is "No. 5508--R & A, OSS." / "13 November 1944." Map includes table: "Reliability of Data." Map shows 6 classes of roads and ports (estimated daily capacity in metric tons).
dct_creator_sm: United States. Office of Strategic Services. Research and Analysis Branch
dct_publisher_sm: [Washington, D. C.] : Office of Strategic Services. Research and Analysis Branch, 1944.
